description.narrative:
The key achievements of the project are:-• The establishment  Program Support Unit at AUC, which is playing the role of coordinating the implementation of entire JLMP on the continent including the Three Years JLMP Priority Action;
•The project demonstrated gender dimension by deliberatley putting three female staff on board out of the total five staff seconded at the AUC Department of Social Affairs at Program Support Unit.
• It also helped to institutionalize JLMP at AUC which other development partners are using as reference for future support to the programme.
